&lt;h2&gt;Role Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring an Affiliate Marketing Specialist to own our affiliate, word-of-mouth, and referral programs. The right person is a data-led growth marketer who knows how to design incentives, structure programs, and turn happy users and motivated partners into compounding, viral loops of new signups and active customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Affiliate program ownership&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end affiliate program — recruitment, onboarding, activation, payouts, and ongoing performance management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a high-quality roster of affiliates across content creators, communities, comparison sites, KOLs, and niche operators relevant to our products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set commission structures, tiers, and incentives that drive the right behaviour without leaking margin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously prune low performers and double down on what is working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Referral and word-of-mouth programs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, launch, and iterate on user referral programs that turn customers into a reliable acquisition channel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build word-of-mouth and ambassador motions that amplify product launches and key moments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create the in-product surfaces, messaging, and reward mechanics that actually get users to share&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Viral loops and growth mechanics&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and build viral loops within and around our products — where each new user predictably drives the next&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run structured experiments on incentives, reward design, sharing surfaces, copy, and timing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map the math of each loop (k-factor, cycle time, payback) and continuously work to improve it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Data, measurement, and reporting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Instrument every program end-to-end so attribution, fraud, and performance are clean and reliable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and track the core KPIs: referred signups, activation rate, CAC, payback, fraud rate, share rate, k-factor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build dashboards that make program health legible to the wider team and inform decisions on spend, incentives, and scope&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively detect and shut down fraud, abuse, and incentive gaming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Cross-functional collaboration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with product and engineering on in-product referral surfaces, tracking, and attribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with finance and compliance on payout structures, KYC/AML, and program terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with the wider growth, content, social, and partnerships teams to amplify programs at launch and on an ongoing basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
