&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years in affiliate, referral, partnerships, or growth marketing with direct ownership of a measurable program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable track record growing a meaningful acquisition channel through affiliates, referrals, or viral loops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong data orientation — comfortable in spreadsheets, BI tools, and attribution platforms, and confident in SQL or willing to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with affiliate platforms (Impact, PartnerStack, Trackier, Everflow, or similar) and referral tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sharp instincts for incentive design — what motivates partners and users without breaking program economics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written English and the ability to recruit, brief, and manage external partners professionally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter mindset, comfortable owning a program end-to-end in a fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
