&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–4 years of experience in a content, copywriting, or social media role, ideally covering both short-form social and long-form written content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrably strong written English. Clear, concise, and credible to an institutional audience&lt;/li&gt;
