&lt;li&gt;Identify performance gaps in individual agents and follow through with targeted coaching plans, not just generic feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate policy updates and guidance from Blockchain.com&#39;s internal team into clear, practical operating instructions for agents&lt;/li&gt;
